---
import LayoutKol from '../../layouts/LayoutKol.astro';
---

<LayoutKol
  title="Estrategia KOL e Influencer"
  description="Sistema KOL de alto impacto. De $100K a $1M anual. Monetiza tu audiencia sin perder el alma con Sebas.co."
  locale="es"
  keywords={["KOL crypto español", "influencer monetización crypto", "programa influencer BingX", "influencer Bitunix", "monetizar audiencia crypto", "revenue sharing influencer", "acceso VIP exchange KOL", "creador contenido web3", "influencer cripto", "sistema KOL alto impacto"]}
>
  <main class="pt-20 flex flex-col items-center w-full">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="relative w-full min-h-[85vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 py-20 text-center bg-[#181611] overflow-hidden">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20 bg-cover bg-center"
        style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1634128221889-82ed6efebfc3?q=80&w=2940&auto=format&fit=crop')"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Patrón geométrico abstracto"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#181611]/80 via-[#181611]/90 to-[#181611]" />
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl flex flex-col gap-6 items-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-[#f2a60d]/30 bg-[#f2a60d]/10 text-[#f2a60d] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#f2a60d] animate-pulse" />
          Sistema KOL de Alto Impacto
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-none tracking-tighter text-white">
          ESTÁS SENTADO SOBRE <br />
          <span class="text-gradient-gold">UNA MINA DE ORO</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 font-light max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          De $100K a $1M anual. Monetiza tu audiencia sin perder el alma con el sistema definitivo de arquitectura de imperio digital.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 mt-8 w-full justify-center">
          <a
            href="#evaluacion"
            class="bg-[#f2a60d] hover:bg-white text-[#181611] text-lg font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(242,166,13,0.3)] text-center"
          >
            Quiero una evaluación gratuita
          </a>
          <a
            href="#testimonios"
            class="border border-[#393328] hover:border-white text-white text-lg font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-all bg-[#27231b]/50 backdrop-blur-sm text-center"
          >
            Ver casos de éxito
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 flex items-center gap-8 text-gray-500 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">
          <span>Auditado</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-gray-600 rounded-full" />
          <span>Validado</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-gray-600 rounded-full" />
          <span>Escalable</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pain Points -->
    <section id="diagnostico" class="w-full bg-[#181611] px-6 py-24 border-t border-[#2a2418]">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end mb-16 gap-6">
          <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-[#f2a60d] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm mb-2">Diagnóstico inicial</h2>
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
              Tu situación actual: <br />El costo de la inacción
            </h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-md text-base md:text-lg">
            La mayoría de los creadores están dejando dinero sobre la mesa por falta de infraestructura, no de talento.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="group glow-effect bg-[#221c10] border border-[#393328] p-8 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#f2a60d]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#f2a60d] mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#f2a60d] group-hover:text-[#181611] transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">schedule</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Desperdicio de tiempo</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Creas contenido sin parar pero los ingresos no escalan con tu esfuerzo. Estás en la rueda del hámster.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="group glow-effect bg-[#221c10] border border-[#393328] p-8 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#f2a60d]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#f2a60d] mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#f2a60d] group-hover:text-[#181611] transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">link_off</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Dependencia</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Tu negocio vive o muere por el algoritmo del día. Si Instagram cambia mañana, tus ingresos desaparecen.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="group glow-effect bg-[#221c10] border border-[#393328] p-8 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#f2a60d]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#f2a60d] mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#f2a60d] group-hover:text-[#181611] transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">trending_down</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">RPM bajo</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Miles de vistas, pero centavos en el banco. Estás monetizando atención barata en vez de influencia real.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="group glow-effect bg-[#221c10] border border-[#393328] p-8 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#f2a60d]/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-[#f2a60d] mb-6 group-hover:bg-[#f2a60d] group-hover:text-[#181611] transition-colors">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">battery_alert</span>
            </div>
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Burnout creativo</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              La presión de publicar diario te está drenando. Necesitas un sistema que venda mientras duermes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- KOL archetypes -->
    <section id="arquetipos" class="w-full bg-[#221c10] px-6 py-24 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-[#f2a60d]/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none" />
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Define tu arquetipo de poder</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">No todos los imperios se construyen igual. Identifica tu fortaleza y la aprovecharemos.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          <div class="relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden rounded-xl h-[400px]">
            <img
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-60"
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?w=800&q=80"
              alt="Gráficos y datos de análisis"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent" />
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6 w-full">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2 text-[#f2a60d]">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">analytics</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Basado en Datos</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">El analista</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm max-h-0 group-hover:max-h-40 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">
                Conviertes datos complejos en insights accionables. Tu audiencia te busca por la verdad.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#f2a60d]" />
          </div>
          <div class="relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden rounded-xl h-[400px]">
            <img
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-60"
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517694712202-14dd9538aa97?w=800&q=80"
              alt="Desarrollo técnico"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent" />
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6 w-full">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2 text-[#f2a60d]">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">code</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Basado en Habilidades</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">El técnico</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm max-h-0 group-hover:max-h-40 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">
                Maestro de la ejecución. Enseñas el "cómo" mejor que nadie. Tu autoridad es incuestionable.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden rounded-xl h-[400px]">
            <img
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-60"
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=800&q=80"
              alt="Comunicación y opinión"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent" />
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6 w-full">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2 text-[#f2a60d]">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">campaign</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Líder de Opinión</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">El provocador</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm max-h-0 group-hover:max-h-40 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">
                Dices lo que otros callan. Polarizas para filtrar tu tribu real y monetizar la lealtad.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative group cursor-pointer overflow-hidden rounded-xl h-[400px]">
            <img
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-40 group-hover:opacity-60"
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522202176988-66273c2fd55f?w=800&q=80"
              alt="Educación y mentoría"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/50 to-transparent" />
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-6 w-full">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2 text-[#f2a60d]">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">school</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Mentor</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">El educador</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm max-h-0 group-hover:max-h-40 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">
                Transformas vidas a través del conocimiento. Tu producto es la claridad y los resultados.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process: Empire building -->
    <section id="proceso" class="w-full bg-[#181611] px-6 py-24 relative">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Construcción del imperio</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400">4 fases de creador a emprendedor digital</p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-[#393328] md:-translate-x-1/2" />
          <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 top-0 h-1/2 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#f2a60d] to-transparent md:-translate-x-1/2" />

          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center mb-16 md:mb-24">
            <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right pl-20 md:pl-0 mb-4 md:mb-0">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">01. Auditoría estratégica</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Inmersión profunda en tu audiencia actual, métricas y fugas de capital. Identificamos tu "Propuesta de Valor Única".</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 w-10 h-10 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-[#181611] border-2 border-[#f2a60d] flex items-center justify-center text-[#f2a60d] z-10">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">search</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 pl-20 hidden md:block" />
          </div>

          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center mb-16 md:mb-24">
            <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 hidden md:block" />
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 w-10 h-10 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-[#181611] border-2 border-[#f2a60d] flex items-center justify-center text-[#f2a60d] z-10 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(242,166,13,0.4)]">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">inventory_2</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 md:text-left pl-20 mb-4 md:mb-0">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">02. Diseño de oferta high-ticket</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Creamos un producto de alto valor irresistible. Dejamos de vender tiempo y empezamos a vender transformación.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center mb-16 md:mb-24">
            <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right pl-20 md:pl-0 mb-4 md:mb-0">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">03. Embudo de conversión</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Ingeniería de ventas automatizada. Email marketing, VSLs y retargeting para convertir desconocidos en clientes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 w-10 h-10 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-[#181611] border-2 border-[#f2a60d] flex items-center justify-center text-[#f2a60d] z-10">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">filter_alt</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 pl-20 hidden md:block" />
          </div>

          <div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center">
            <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 hidden md:block" />
            <div class="absolute left-8 md:left-1/2 w-10 h-10 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-[#f2a60d] text-[#181611] flex items-center justify-center z-10">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm font-bold">rocket_launch</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 w-full md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 md:text-left pl-20 mb-4 md:mb-0">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">04. Automatización y escala</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Sistemas que funcionan sin ti. Delegación de operaciones y enfoque en el crecimiento exponencial.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Revenue Projection -->
    <section class="w-full bg-[#221c10] px-6 py-24 border-y border-[#393328]">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Proyección realista de ingresos</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 text-lg">
              Basado en una audiencia de 50k–100k seguidores con un engagement promedio del 3%.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#f2a60d]">check_circle</span>
                Sin dependencia de marcas
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#f2a60d]">check_circle</span>
                Márgenes de ganancia &gt; 80%
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#f2a60d]">check_circle</span>
                Control total de tu base de datos
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a
              href="#evaluacion"
              class="bg-[#f2a60d] hover:bg-white text-[#181611] font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2"
            >
              Calcular mi potencial
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1 w-full bg-[#181611] rounded-xl border border-[#393328] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
            <div class="bg-[#2a2418] px-6 py-4 border-b border-[#393328] flex justify-between items-center">
              <span class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">Panel de Ingresos</span>
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500" />
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500" />
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-left min-w-[320px]">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#393328]">
                    <th class="pb-4 text-gray-500 font-medium text-sm">Fase</th>
                    <th class="pb-4 text-gray-500 font-medium text-sm">Producto</th>
                    <th class="pb-4 text-right text-gray-500 font-medium text-sm">Ingreso mensual</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-gray-300">
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#393328]/50">
                    <td class="py-4">Inicio</td>
                    <td class="py-4">AdSense / Afiliados</td>
                    <td class="py-4 text-right font-mono text-gray-500">$500 - $2,000</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#393328]/50">
                    <td class="py-4">Fase 1</td>
                    <td class="py-4">Consultoría 1:1</td>
                    <td class="py-4 text-right font-mono">$3,000 - $8,000</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-[#393328]/50">
                    <td class="py-4 text-[#f2a60d] font-bold">Fase 2</td>
                    <td class="py-4 text-white">Curso cohort (high ticket)</td>
                    <td class="py-4 text-right font-mono text-[#f2a60d] font-bold">$15,000 - $40,000</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-4 text-[#f2a60d] font-bold">Escala</td>
                    <td class="py-4 text-white">Ecosistema completo</td>
                    <td class="py-4 text-right font-mono text-[#f2a60d] font-bold text-lg">$50,000 - $100,000+</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonios -->
    <section id="testimonios" class="w-full bg-[#181611] px-6 py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-16">Ya escalaron su influencia</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-[#221c10] p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#393328] relative text-left">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[#393328] absolute top-6 right-6">format_quote</span>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <img
                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover border border-[#f2a60d]"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=96&h=96&fit=crop&crop=face"
                alt="Carlos M."
                width="48"
                height="48"
              />
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold">Carlos M.</h4>
                <p class="text-[#f2a60d] text-xs uppercase font-bold">Finanzas personales</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm italic">
              "Pasé de cobrar $50 por post a cerrar deals recurrentes de $5k mensuales con mi propia comunidad. Sebas.co cambió completamente mi mentalidad."
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#221c10] p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#f2a60d]/40 relative text-left shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(242,166,13,0.1)]">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[#f2a60d]/20 absolute top-6 right-6">format_quote</span>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <img
                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover border border-[#f2a60d]"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?w=96&h=96&fit=crop&crop=face"
                alt="Ana S."
                width="48"
                height="48"
              />
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold">Ana S.</h4>
                <p class="text-[#f2a60d] text-xs uppercase font-bold">Coach de fitness</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm italic">
              "Tenía 200k seguidores y estaba en quiebra. En 3 meses implementamos el embudo high-ticket y facturé mis primeros $25k. Simplemente brutal."
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-[#221c10] p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#393328] relative text-left">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-[#393328] absolute top-6 right-6">format_quote</span>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <img
                class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover border border-[#f2a60d]"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1472099645785-5658abf4ff4e?w=96&h=96&fit=crop&crop=face"
                alt="David R."
